title: [Translated from German] From the Street to the Museum! Check ✅ Ten years ago, we launched "Right Against Right." Today, we are delighted to announce that our campaign is part of the exhibition "After Hitler: Germany's Confrontation with National Socialism" at the House of History in Bonn!
